N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 921-7.7 - Admissibility of decision or order

State Regulations

No decision or order issued pursuant to this Act shall be
admissible or used in evidence in any subsequent court proceeding except in an
action by the Commissioner or the employer to implement, enforce or challenge a
determination made by the Commissioner pursuant to this Act. Notes
